1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Here we are in the central control room where the 
boiler operators monitor and control the boilers.  

2
00:00:05,760 --> 00:00:10,080
This state-of-the-art control system 
has been in place since 2021 and uses  

3
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:15,360
program logic controller or PLC technology 
along with a system of cameras and sensors.  

4
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:21,300
These interactive screens give the boiler operator 
an overview of the entire system in real time,  

5
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:25,680
including states and measurements 
of air, water, steam, and fuel.

6
00:00:26,580 --> 00:00:30,300
They also make the control and 
operation of valves more accurate,  

7
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:32,820
efficient, reliable, and user-friendly.

